import { Grid, Card, CardHeader, CardContent } from "@material-ui/core"
import { DirectionsBus } from "@material-ui/icons"

const BusesComponent =()=>{
    return(
        <Card>
            <CardHeader
            title={'Buses'}
            avatar={<DirectionsBus/>}/>
            <CardContent>
                <Grid container spacing={2}>
                    <Grid item md={3}>
                        List
                    </Grid>

                    <Grid item md={9}>
                        View
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </CardContent>
        </Card>
    )
}
export default BusesComponent
